    <dashboard _.fcp.AccessibleZoneTabOrder.true...enable-sort-zone-taborder='true' name='Overview'>
      <repository-location derived-from='https://tableaudev.cotiviti.com/t/OpportunityIntelligence/workbooks/PPMPolicyGapAnalysis_17325237718210/Overview?rev=' id='28715' path='/t/OpportunityIntelligence/workbooks/PPMPolicyGapAnalysis_17325237718210' revision='' site='OpportunityIntelligence' />
      <style>
        <style-rule element='table'>
          <format attr='background-color' value='#00000000' />
        </style-rule>
        <style-rule element='dash-title'>
          <format attr='text-align' value='center' />
          <format attr='background-color' value='#30006f' />
          <format attr='color' value='#ffffff' />
          <format attr='font-family' value='Tableau Medium' />
        </style-rule>
        <style-rule element='dash-text'>
          <format attr='text-align' value='center' />
        </style-rule>
        <style-rule element='parameter-ctrl'>
          <format attr='color' value='#000000' />
          <format attr='font-weight' value='normal' />
          <format attr='font-size' value='10' />
          <format attr='font-family' value='Tableau Medium' />
          <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
          <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
          <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
          <format attr='background-color' value='#e6e6e6' />
        </style-rule>
        <style-rule element='parameter-ctrl-title'>
          <format attr='text-align' value='left' />
          <format attr='font-weight' value='normal' />
          <format attr='font-family' value='Tableau Bold' />
          <format attr='font-size' value='12' />
          <format attr='color' value='#36006f' />
        </style-rule>
      </style>
      <size sizing-mode='automatic' />
      <zones>
        <zone h='100000' id='4' type-v2='layout-basic' w='100000' x='0' y='0'>
          <zone h='88938' id='298' param='vert' type-v2='layout-flow' w='100000' x='0' y='7522'>
            <zone fixed-size='254' forceUpdate='true' h='28982' id='595' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='100000' x='0' y='7522'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#31006f' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='18'>Report Description</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>This data product enables users to filter and prioritize opportunities by leveraging benchmark data from other clients. It identifies key opportunities for each client by comparing their metrics to similar clients who have demonstrated positive adoption trends.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Primary Benefits:</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='16'>· </run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>It highlights opportunities where a client lags competition on policy adoption.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='16'>· </run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>It promotes compliance where other government payers are on edits while target payer isn’t. </run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='16'>· </run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>It Includes ability to do a broader gap analysis on common dimensions including LOB, state, Blues, and customer segment.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                <format attr='padding-left' value='30' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
            <zone fixed-size='404' forceUpdate='true' h='45575' id='1042' is-fixed='true' type-v2='text' w='100000' x='0' y='36504'>
              <formatted-text>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#9579d3' fontname='Tableau Bold' fontsize='18'>Tab Description</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Policy Gap Analysis:</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>This view displays Opportunity DPs on common dimensions including LOB, Blues and Customer Segment. </run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>Policy Gap Analysis - State Level:</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>This view displays Opportunity DPs on common dimensions including LOB, State, Blues and Customer Segment </run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>How to Use the Tool:</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>1. Start by setting the desired filters, such as choosing your specific customer or payer short.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>2. Use the Dimension filters to select your desired benchmark level, ranging from broad to highly targeted dimensions.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>3. Adjust the ‘Customer Adoption Rate’ and ‘Payer Adoption Rate’ sliders to set your minimum adoption percentage thresholds. You can either use the slider or manually input your desired percentage.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>4. The tool will return Decision Points (DPs) that meet or exceed the benchmark adoption percentages you’ve specified.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontsize='14'>5. To export the view to Excel, select “Crosstab” and choose the appropriate layout: PGA-CS for customer level, PGA-SP for super payer level, or PGA-PS for payer short level of display.</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
              </formatted-text>
              <zone-style>
                <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                <format attr='padding-left' value='30' />
              </zone-style>
            </zone>
